org.apache.juddi.v3_service

Interface JUDDIApiPortType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JUDDIApiImpl, JUDDIApiService

    public interface JUDDIApiPortType
    This portType defines all of the jUDDI publisher operations. This is above and beyond the original UDDI v3 specification and is NOT part of the standard. Method behavior within this class may change from version to version. These methods are primarily meant for administrative functions. This class was generated by the JAX-WS RI. JAX-WS RI 2.2.4-b01 Generated source version: 2.2
